Package: no-overview-gnome-shell-extension
Architecture: all
Depends: gnome-shell (>= 45~), ${misc:Depends}
Description: No overview at start-up GNOME Shell Extension
 A GNOME Shell extension that hides the overview screen on startup.
 Prevents the Activities overview from appearing when GNOME Shell starts.
